The paper deals with designing a lightweight and robust portrait segmentation algorithm, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also introduces a new model architecture and proposes a method to create additional data, which involves machine learning techniques (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also discusses the execution of the model on a real mobile device, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) and computer systems and networking (cs.CR).
